Airgapped Key Ceremony Buildroot Image

Primary workflow:

  1) Connect YubiKey and printer (usblp).
  2) Run: ./rsa-keygen.sh
  3) Mount USB media: ./mount-usb.sh

Networking is disabled by default.
Verify airgap (simple checks):

  Interfaces/routing:
    ip a
    ip r
  Open sockets:
    netstat
  Root fs is tmpfs:
    df -hT
  See all devices:
    find /sys/class


